                    <p>This project is a complete E-Commerce project. With some small changes it can be used for commercial usage.</p>

                    <h2>Functionality</h2>

                    <p>
                        User in this application is able to: <br /><br />
                        - Create account<br />
                        - Login <br />
                        - Edit/Delete account<br />
                        - Add/Remove/Update items from the baset<br />
                        - Send message to administration<br />
                        - When sending order will recieve information about the order<br /><br />

                        Administrator of this application is able to: <br /><br />
                        - Manage products (create/edit/delete/update stock)<br />
                        - Website is shocasing stock status (low/out of stock messages are beeing displayed)<br />
                        - Add/Remove/Edit suppliers<br />
                        - Send orders to the registered suppliers<br />
                        - Manage user accounts. Change if e-mail/phone confirmation is nesecary for the registration. Ban accounts.<br />
                        - See sales, orders, income, users, company orders statistics<br />
                        - Use built in CMS to edit content of the pages (Main Page)<br />
                        - Create team accounts<br />
                        - Team can use built in chat app, notes board, email<br />
                        <br />
                    </p>

